/p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">公司成立于一九九七年十月。多年来，积累了广泛的社会信誉，得到了各级主管部门、社会各界及消费者的广泛赞誉，先后获得&ldquo;放心食品&rdquo;、&ldquo;重点保护品牌&rdquo;、&ldquo;重点推荐食品&rdquo;等近百项国家和省市级荣誉及称号。多年来，经各级技术监督、卫生防疫、工商管理及商检部门几百次抽查检验，从未发现不合格产品。被山东省政府认定为&ldquo;山东省农业产业化重点龙头企业&rdquo;、&ldquo;山东省农产品加工示范企业&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">公司立足当地环境及农产品资源优势，坚持不懈的生产加工高品质产品，拥有&ldquo;长思&rdquo;、&ldquo;奥赛&rdquo;两大品牌。于2008年投资创建集良种鸡鸭生态养殖、现代化屠宰、调理品和熟食加工为一体的大型企业，通过了ISO14001环境管理体系认证，被农业部农产品质量安全中心认定为&ldquo;无公害农产品&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2015年公司与教育部直属全国重点大学、国家肉制品加工与质量安全控制权威机构&mdash;南京农业大学结成产学研战略合作伙伴，深入推进产品研发和创新，建设高标准研发和实验基地，并于当年合作推出健康美味的&ldquo;恋上鸭&rdquo;休闲鸭肉系列产品。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&ldquo;恋上鸭&rdquo;产品原料全部来自于&ldquo;生态畜牧区&rdquo;公司自有生态养殖基地和现代化屠宰工厂，全程追溯严格监测。现宰直送，不需冷冻，科学预冷，鲜烹鲜制。采用上等天然植物香辛料，拒绝麻辣香精，健康自然。现代化高标准的全封闭净化车间，先进设备，科学工艺，专属配方，透明生产，最大程度的确保了产品的安全和健康、美味与营养。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&ldquo;恋上鸭&rdquo;产品原料新鲜，产品新鲜，真材实料，特点明显，麻辣鲜香，竞争力强。健源公司有信心、有实力与全国经销商朋友携手打造休闲鸭肉产品强势品牌并为大家带来良好回报。</span></p>\r\n<div><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br />\r\n</span></div>');
INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('5807','<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; text-align: center;\">产品简介</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;日盛牌桔子罐头，公司从事出口生产多年，产品远销欧洲，美国，加拿大，日本等发达国家地区，产品质量通过各项国外认证，如：FDA(美国食品药品监督局认证)；BRC(英国零售商协会认证)；KOSHER(犹太洁食认证)；HACCP食品安全控制体系等。国内销售的罐头与出口的罐头均为同一流水线生产，所有罐头均按照出口标准生产。产品由桔子，白糖，水，柠檬酸(酸度调节剂)制作而成，绝不含防腐剂，绝不含甜蜜素，绝不含色素，绝不含农残，绝不含BPA(双酚A)。定位于对食品安全重视的人群。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">产品卖点</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">本公司产品远销国外多年，且以发达国家地区为主要，得到国外客商的认可，产品质量及理念远超国内同类产品，产品由桔子，白糖，水，柠檬酸(酸度调节剂)制作而成，绝不含防腐剂，绝不含甜蜜素，绝不含色素，绝不含农残，绝不含BPA(双酚A)。相比新鲜的桔子，桔子罐头营养价值更高，因为任何蔬果在采摘后都仍在继续&ldquo;呼吸&rdquo;，一些营养素会不断减少。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">而桔子罐头从原料采摘到加工好的全过程不超过24小时，高温热处理会停止或减缓营养损失的化学反应，保持食物的鲜度和营养。桔子采摘一天后，维生素C会损失30%，而桔子罐头则只损失10%。因此，比起长途运输的&ldquo;新鲜&rdquo;桔子，桔子罐头反而更&ldquo;新鲜&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: